      <abstract>
        <p>Roundup of recent advertising account changes (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>* Prestige Brands International, Bonita Springs, Fla., to Harris Drury Cohen, Fort Lauderdale, Fla., to handle the account for its Chloraseptic throat spray and lozenges, which had been at D'Arcy Masius Benton &amp; Bowles, New York, part of the B Com3  Group, when the brand was still owned by Procter &amp; Gamble. Spending was estimated at $4 million to $5 million.</p>
      </block>
